---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="關於艷世 | YENZ Design" description="艷世設計的品牌故事、設計哲學與核心價值。">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="page-hero-label">ABOUT</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">遇見艷世</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Explore YENZ</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Brand Story -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="about-intro reveal">
      <div class="about-intro-content">
        <h2 class="about-title">設計，是將理念<br>精雕為現實的藝術。</h2>
        <div class="about-divider"></div>
        <p class="about-text">
          2016年，創辦人懷抱著讓世界為之驚艷的溫暖初心，在台北創立了艷世設計。
          她深信，每一個品牌都蘊含著獨特的生命力與故事，值得被以最精緻、最富內涵的方式演繹。
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          真正的設計，不僅是視覺的驚鴻一瞥，它更是一場情感的觸動，
          一份能經得起時間淬鍊，恆久流傳的經典。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- The Eternal Knot -->
  <section class="section section-gradient">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-number">01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">THE ETERNAL KNOT</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">永恆之結</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="knot-section reveal">
      <div class="knot-visual">
        <div class="knot-circle">
          <span class="knot-symbol">Y</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="knot-content">
        <p class="knot-intro">
          YENZ 的品牌印記，不僅是品牌首字母 Y 的優雅化身，<br>
          它更是一個視覺化的哲學——一個生生不息的「永恆之結」。
        </p>
        
        <div class="knot-meanings">
          <div class="knot-meaning reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <h3>策略與美學的無限對話</h3>
            <p>卓越的設計源於策略與美學的緊密結合，兩者相互依存、彼此成就。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="knot-meaning reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <h3>根基與綻放的品牌生命力</h3>
            <p>繩結的底部穩固而緊密，象徵品牌奠定的堅實策略根基，代表價值的無限延伸。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="knot-meaning reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <h3>信任與共創的永恆夥伴</h3>
            <p>與客戶之間建立在信任與共創之上的永恆夥伴關係。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Three Promises -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-number">02</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">OUR PROMISES</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">艷世設計三大承諾</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="promises-grid">
      <div class="promise-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="promise-number">01</div>
        <h3 class="promise-title">獨家匠造，彰顯唯一</h3>
        <p class="promise-desc">
          您的品牌值得擁有獨一無二的視覺符號。我們不追逐制式，亦不複製短暫流行，
          透過深度對談，傾聽您的品牌故事與願景，為您量身定制的藝術創作。
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="promise-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="promise-number">02</div>
        <h3 class="promise-title">智慧結晶，專屬歸屬</h3>
        <p class="promise-desc">
          您在艷世所孕育的每一件設計，其完整的著作財產權將毫無保留地歸您所有。
          我們堅持透明公開，絕無任何隱藏或分段收費，讓您的權益一次到位。
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="promise-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="promise-number">03</div>
        <h3 class="promise-title">專屬顧問，品牌遠航</h3>
        <p class="promise-desc">
          品牌發展是持續的旅程。無論未來您的品牌在應用推廣或發展上遇到任何疑問，
          艷世的專業團隊都將是您最堅實的後盾。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- AI Statement -->
  <section class="section section-gradient">
    <div class="ai-statement reveal">
      <div class="ai-icon">◈</div>
      <h2 class="ai-title">前瞻思維，智慧偕行</h2>
      <p class="ai-subtitle">與時俱進：我們對 AI 應用的責任與承諾</p>
      <div class="ai-divider"></div>
      <p class="ai-text">
        在人工智慧浪潮席捲設計領域的今日，艷世設計擁抱創新，同時堅守對智慧財產權的最高標準。
        我們使用如 Adobe Firefly 等專為商業用途設計、確保素材來源合規的 AI 模型，
        並搭配 Envato Elements 的正版授權素材。
      </p>
      <p class="ai-text">
        我們向您保證，交付的每一件作品，其創意與版權皆清晰、穩固，
        讓您能安心地將品牌託付給我們。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Company Info -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="company-info reveal">
      <h2 class="company-title">艷世設計有限公司</h2>
      <p class="company-subtitle">YENZ Design Studio Co., Ltd.</p>
      <div class="company-details">
        <div class="company-detail">
          <span class="detail-label">統一編號</span>
          <span class="detail-value">83515285</span>
        </div>
        <div class="company-detail">
          <span class="detail-label">成立日期</span>
          <span class="detail-value">民國 109 年 3 月</span>
        </div>
        <div class="company-detail">
          <span class="detail-label">登記機關</span>
          <span class="detail-value">臺北市政府</span>
        </div>
        <div class="company-detail">
          <span class="detail-label">公司地址</span>
          <span class="detail-value">臺北市信義區忠孝東路五段482號15樓之4</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--forest-darkest) 0%, var(--forest-dark) 100%);
    padding-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .page-hero-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .page-hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  
  /* About Intro */
  .about-intro {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }
  
  .about-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .about-divider {
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  
  .about-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  /* Knot Section */
  .knot-section {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .knot-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .knot-circle {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .knot-circle::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 240px;
    height: 240px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  
  .knot-symbol {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  
  .knot-intro {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .knot-meanings {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .knot-meaning h3 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .knot-meaning p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  /* Promises */
  .promises-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .promise-card {
    background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
  }
  
  .promise-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  
  .promise-number {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .promise-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .promise-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1.9;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  /* AI Statement */
  .ai-statement {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  
  .ai-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .ai-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .ai-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .ai-divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  
  .ai-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  /* Company Info */
  .company-info {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .company-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .company-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .company-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .company-detail {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1);
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .detail-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .detail-value {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }
  
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .knot-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .promises-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .company-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
